{"id": "1319153828553035786", "channel_id": "1319153828553035786", "author_id": "139343733714845697", "author_name": "satachan", "content": "During the loading screen there is a lot of lore text that has never been archived before.\nWhile it would be cool for the devs to give it to us, I think it would be even better if we can do it on our own.\nIf you have text on your loading screen that hasn't been posted here, please do so!\n\nI will transcribe the text for you \n\n\"Some Corrosive Bodies turn into black power after death, known as Corrosive Dust.\"", "timestamp": "2024-12-19T04:06:21.420000+00:00", "thread_id": "1319153828553035786", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-19T04:10:09.170000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1319154001224138883", "filename": "Screenshot_20241219_110636_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 53041, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1319153828553035786/1319154001224138883/Screenshot_20241219_110636_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc99e6&is=69cb4866&hm=d089aa7be715744f7730a106ca2a0bbd1d96ffacd8d73b13ae1ec35a6d70513b&"}]}
{"id": "1319154339184644116", "channel_id": "1319153828553035786", "author_id": "139343733714845697", "author_name": "satachan", "content": "\"When the Corrosive Phenomenon appears on a material, it manifests as one or several small inverted triangular holes. These holes range in size from about 3 mm to 1 cm, and as the Corrosion progresses, the Corrosive marks will gradually expand\"", "timestamp": "2024-12-19T04:08:23.164000+00:00", "thread_id": "1319153828553035786", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-19T04:09:56.934000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1319154338970472539", "filename": "Screenshot_20241219_110803_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 59325, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1319153828553035786/1319154338970472539/Screenshot_20241219_110803_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc9a37&is=69cb48b7&hm=ac598c3ed0d7132eee69eebf2ec51c5a4fc88cff6c6ac1332feef60e406098ed&"}]}
